ues|\n{{no footnotes|date=August 2015}}\n{{third-party|date=August 2015}}\n}}\n\n{{Infobox University\n|name         = Institute of Foreign Languages<br><small>Institut des langues \u00e9trang\u00e8res</small>\n|native_name  = \u179c\u17b7\u1791\u17d2\u1799\u17b6\u179f\u17d2\u1790\u17b6\u1793\u1797\u17b6\u179f\u17b6\u1794\u179a\u1791\u17c1\u179f\n|image        = Institute of Foreign Languages.png \n|motto        = \n|established  = 1985 \n|parent       = [[Royal University of Phnom Penh]] \n|type         = [[National university|National]]\n|director     = Meas Vanna\n|address      = Russian Federation Boulevard\n|city         = [[Phnom Penh]]\n|country      = [[Cambodia]]\n|free_label   = Social\n|free         = [https://www.facebook.com/rupp.edu.kh Facebook]\n|coor         = {{coord|11.569|104.8914|region:KH-12_type:landmark|display=inline,title}}\n|colors       = \n|undergrad    =\n|postgrad     =\n|students     = \n|staff        = \n|faculty      =\n|endowment    = \n|affiliations = [[ASEAN University Network]]<br />[[Agence Universitaire de la Francophonie]]\n|nickname     = IFL\n|website      = {{URL|http://www.rupp.edu.kh/ifl/}}\n}}\n{{Contains Khmer text}}\n\nThe '''Institute of Foreign Languages''' ('''IFL''') ({{lang-km|\u179c\u17b7\u1791\u17d2\u1799\u17b6\u179f\u17d2\u1790\u17b6\u1793\u1797\u17b6\u179f\u17b6\u1794\u179a\u1791\u17c1\u179f}}) is an institution under [[Royal University of Phnom Penh]] Campus. It consists of the following departments :\n* Chinese\n* English\n* French\n* Thai\n* Korean\n* Japanese\n* International Studies\n\n== See also ==\n* [[List of universities in Cambodia]]\n* [[Royal University of Phnom Penh]]\n\n== External links ==\n* [http://www.rupp.edu.kh/ifl/ Official Website of IFL]\n\n\n\n[[Category:Universities and colleges in Cambodia]]\n[[Category:Schools in Phnom Penh]]\n[[Category:Language schools]]\n", "name_user": "Ser Amantio di Nicolao", "label": "safe", "comment": "add authority control", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/